== 门票销售 ==
[[国际足联|国际足联]]预计本届锦标赛共售出3，334，524张门票<ref name="Tickets">{{cite web|url=http://www.fifa.com/mm/document/tournament/ticketing/02/12/19/77/fwc2014-ticket-media-info-en_neutral.pdf|title=Ticket media information|publisher=FIFA|format=PDF|accessdate=6 December 2013|archive-date=2018-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181103070137/https://www.fifa.com/mm/document/tournament/ticketing/02/12/19/77/fwc2014-ticket-media-info-en_neutral.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>，其中大部分分配给商务合作伙伴、客户接待、贵宾、媒体版权持有人<ref name="Tickets"/>。约110万门票面向公众销售，其中40万提供给巴西民众、70人供给海外<ref name="Tickets"/>，8%预留给参赛球队的球迷<ref name="2nd phase">{{cite web|url=http://www.fifa.com/worldcup/news/y=2014/m=1/news=more-than-million-tickets-for-brazil-2014-requested-second-sales-phase-2267462.html|title=Over 3.5 million tickets requested in second sales phase|publisher=FIFA|date=30 January 2014|accessdate=2014-07-04|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303183504/http://www.fifa.com/worldcup/news/y=2014/m=1/news=more-than-million-tickets-for-brazil-2014-requested-second-sales-phase-2267462.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。门票销售分为三个阶段，公众可以登录国际足联官网订票，或是前往各主办城市指定地点购票<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.fifa.com/worldcup/organisation/ticketing/ticket-information/sale-phases/index.html|title=Sales phases|publisher=FIFA|date=20 August 2013|accessdate=2014-07-04|archive-date=2014-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140709040047/http://www.fifa.com/worldcup/organisation/ticketing/ticket-information/sale-phases/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.fifa.com/worldcup/organisation/ticketing/news/newsid=2152054/index.html|title=FIFA Venue Ticketing Centre Locations|publisher=FIFA|date=20 August 2013|accessdate=2014-07-04|archive-date=2019-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190318224439/https://www.fifa.com/worldcup/organisation/ticketing/news/newsid=2152054/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。四类门票中的第四类特供巴西民众<ref name="Tickets"/>。巴西国内60岁以上人士、学生和困难户购买门票可享受优惠<ref name="Tickets"/>。最便宜的门票价格为30[[巴西亚雷尔|巴西亚雷尔]]（约12.5美元），最贵的门票是决赛日的一类票，售价高达999美元<ref name="Tickets"/>。除了单场票，还有可以观看任意一主办城市全部比赛的“指定场地票”和观看某一球队全程比赛的“团队票”<ref name="Tickets"/>。第一阶段销售于2013年8月20日开始，2013年10月，开售当天共售出230万张<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.fifa.com/worldcup/organisation/ticketing/news/newsid=2156005/index.html|title=2.3 million tickets for the FIFA World Cup requested in the first 24 hours of sales|publisher=FIFA|date=22 August 2013|accessdate=2014-07-04|archive-date=2014-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140709040053/http://www.fifa.com/worldcup/organisation/ticketing/news/newsid=2156005/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，全阶段销量超600万张<ref name="#1">{{cite web|url=http://www.fifa.com/worldcup/organisation/ticketing/news/newsid=2193401/index.html|title=Tickets for Brazil 2014 in heavy demand|publisher=FIFA|date=10 October 2013|accessdate=2014-07-04|archive-date=2014-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140709040057/http://www.fifa.com/worldcup/organisation/ticketing/news/newsid=2193401/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。由于门票供不应求，国际足联将889305票抽签分配<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.fifa.com/worldcup/organisation/ticketing/news/newsid=2218428/index.html|title=889,305 tickets allocated during the random selection draw for the 2014 FIFA World Cup|publisher=FIFA|date=5 November 2013|accessdate=2014-07-04|archive-date=2014-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140709040058/http://www.fifa.com/worldcup/organisation/ticketing/news/newsid=2218428/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年11月抢票阶段期间，7小时共售出22万张<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.fifa.com/worldcup/organisation/ticketing/news/newsid=2220909/index.html|title=Second ticketing sales window now open|publisher=FIFA|date=8 November 2013|accessdate=2014-07-04|archive-date=2014-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140709040059/http://www.fifa.com/worldcup/organisation/ticketing/news/newsid=2220909/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.fifa.com/worldcup/organisation/ticketing/news/newsid=2222446/index.html|title=No more 2014 FIFA World Cup tickets available in second sale period after seven hours|publisher=FIFA|date=11 November 2013|accessdate=2014-07-04|archive-date=2014-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140709040104/http://www.fifa.com/worldcup/organisation/ticketing/news/newsid=2222446/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年12月决赛圈抽签后，第二阶段的销售正式开始，吸引超过350万宗申请<ref name="2nd phase"/>，余票自2014年3月起可前往国际足联指定售票网点购买<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.fifa.com/worldcup/news/y=2014/m=3/news=2014-fifa-world-cuptm-tickets-for-matches-sale-from-wednesday-march-12h0-2295532.html|title=Tickets for 60 matches on sale from 12 March at 12.00 CET|publisher=FIFA|date=11 March 2014|accessdate=2014-07-04|archive-date=2014-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140709021937/http://www.fifa.com/worldcup/news/y=2014/m=3/news=2014-fifa-world-cuptm-tickets-for-matches-sale-from-wednesday-march-12h0-2295532.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。2014年4月15日起，全数余票以先购先得原则提供<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.fifa.com/worldcup/news/y=2014/m=4/news=last-ticketing-sales-phase-to-open-on-15-april-at-12h00-cet-2319228.html|title=Last ticketing sales phase to open on 15 April at 12h00 CET|publisher=FIFA|date=14 April 2014|accessdate=2014-07-04|archive-date=2014-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140709021838/http://www.fifa.com/worldcup/news/y=2014/m=4/news=last-ticketing-sales-phase-to-open-on-15-april-at-12h00-cet-2319228.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。尽管申请期间出现两宗超额的预购申请<ref name="#1"/><ref name="2nd phase"/>，但比赛开始后仍留有小组赛门票<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.fifa.com/worldcup/news/y=2014/m=6/news=close-to-180-000-tickets-for-the-2014-fifa-world-cup-will-be-up-for-sa-2353399.html|title=Close to 180,000 tickets for the 2014 FIFA World Cup will be up for sale this Wednesday, 4 June|publisher=FIFA|date=2 June 2014|accessdate=2014-07-04|archive-date=2014-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140704161828/http://www.fifa.com/worldcup/news/y=2014/m=6/news=close-to-180-000-tickets-for-the-2014-fifa-world-cup-will-be-up-for-sa-2353399.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

